data.description: Welcome to Golden Gate Estates! This 3 bedroom/ 2 bathroom Single Family Residence is nestled in the middle of paradise. The large 1.14 acre lot provides endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. Located nearby, you will find high-end shopping destinations such as 5th Avenue South, Third Street South, Waterside Shops, Mercato and The Village Shops on Venetian Bay. The beautiful Naples Pier Beach, Seagate Beach and Clam Pass Park are just a short distance away. Food enthusiasts will discover over 700 restaurants to choose from. With over 90 golf courses in the area, golf enthusiasts will find true bliss. Within a 8-minute drive, you will find the neighborhood Publix and YMCA. Vineyards Elementary, Oakridge Middle, and Golden Gate High are part of the school district
